 generation\n- No major migrations needed (pure JDBC)\n\n**11. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirectDBUtils.java**\n- Database utilities for building/resetting database\n- MIGRATION: @Resource DataSource -> @Inject AgroalDataSource\n\n**12. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirect.java**\n- Large file (1807 lines) - Direct JDBC implementation of TradeServices\n- MIGRATION: JMS -> MessageProducerService for messaging\n- MIGRATION: ManagedExecutorService -> CDI Event async for market summary\n- Uses QuarkusTransaction for transaction management\n\n### EJB3 Implementation (JPA)\n\n**13. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java**\n- MIGRATION: @Stateless -> @ApplicationScoped CDI bean\n- MIGRATION: @TransactionAttribute -> @Transactional\n- MIGRATION: JMS -> MessageProducerService\n- Primary TradeServices implementation with @Default qualifier\n\n**14. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java**\n- MIGRATION: @Singleton EJB -> @ApplicationScoped CDI\n- MIGRATION: @Schedule -> @Scheduled (Quarkus)\n- MIGRATION: @Lock -> synchronized methods\n- Periodic market summary updates every 20 seconds\n\n**15. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java**\n- MIGRATION: ManagedScheduledExecutorService -> Quarkus ExecutorService\n- Uses virtual threads for async order processing\n- 500ms delay before processing\n\n**16. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java**\n- Runnable for async order completion\n- Uses CDI @Any Instance for dynamic service selection\n\n### Messaging (JMS -> Reactive Messaging)\n\n**17. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/QuoteUpdateMessage.java**\n- POJO replacing JMS TextMessage for quote updates\n- Commands: \"updateQuote\" and \"ping\"\n- Factory methods for message creation\n\n**18. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/OrderMessage.java**\n- POJO replacing JMS TextMessage for orders\n- Commands: \"neworder\" and \"ping\"\n- Type-safe alternative to JMS properties\n\n**19. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessageProducerService.java**\n- Central service for sending messages\n- MIGRATION: JMS ConnectionFactory/Queue/Topic -> SmallRye Reactive Messaging Emitter\n- @Channel annotations for queue and topic destinations\n- Much cleaner than JMS code (no manual connection management)\n\n### Message-Driven Beans (MDB -> Reactive Messaging)\n\n**20. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTStreamer3MDB.java**\n- MIGRATION: @MessageDriven -> @ApplicationScoped with @Incoming\n- MIGRATION: MessageListener.onMessage(Message) -> method accepting QuoteUpdateMessage POJO\n- Processes quote update streams and ping messages\n- Records timing statistics\n\n**21. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTBroker3MDB.java**\n- MIGRATION: @MessageDriven -> @ApplicationScoped with @Incoming\n- MIGRATION: @Transactional replaces @TransactionAttribute\n- Processes trade orders asynchronously\n- Records MDB statistics\n\n### JAX-RS Resources (REST APIs)\n\n**22. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/TradeResource.java**\n- Main REST API at /rest/trade\n- Endpoints for login, logout, buy, sell, account, portfolio, etc.\n- MIGRATION: javax.ws.rs -> jakarta.ws.rs\n\n**23. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/QuoteResource.java**\n- REST API for quote lookups at /rest/quotes\n- Supports both GET and POST with multiple symbols\n\n**24. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/MessagingResource.java**\n- REST API for messaging testing at /rest/messaging\n- Replaces PingServlet2MDBQueue and PingServlet2MDBTopic\n- Endpoints: /ping/broker, /ping/streamer, /stats\n\n### Interfaces & Annotations\n\n**25-33. Interface files:**\n- TradeSession2Direct.java - CDI Qualifier\n- TradeServices.java - Main service interface\n- TradeJDBC.java - CDI Qualifier for JDBC implementation\n- TradeDB.java - Database utility interface\n- Trace.java - Interceptor binding annotation\n- TradeEJB.java - CDI Qualifier for EJB implementation\n- RuntimeMode.java - CDI Qualifier with mode name\n- QuotePriceChange.java - CDI Qualifier for events\n- MarketSummaryUpdate.java - CDI Qualifier for events\n\n### Session-to-Direct Implementation\n\n**34. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/session2direct/DirectSLSBBean.java**\n- MIGRATION: @Stateless -> @ApplicationScoped\n- Delegates to TradeDirect with inSession flag set\n- Uses @TradeSession2Direct qualifier\n\n### Web Layer\n\n**35. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/TradeAppResource.java**\n- MIGRATION: Servlet -> JAX-RS Resource at /rest/app\n- Simple HTML generation (production would use Qute templates)\n- Handles login, portfolio, account, buy/sell operations\n\n### Startup & Configuration\n\n**36. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/startup/DatabasePopulator.java**\n- Populates database on startup with quotes and users\n- Observes StartupEvent with @Transactional\n- Configurable via application.properties\n\n### Utility Classes\n\n**37-44. Utility files:**\n- TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java - CDI qualifier literal for runtime mode selection\n- TradeConfig.java - Central configuration class (400+ lines)\n- TimerStat.java - Statistics tracking for timing measurements\n- RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java - Tracks last 5 quote changes\n- MDBStats.java - MDB statistics collection (extends HashMap)\n- Log.java - Logging utility (java.util.logging)\n- KeyBlock.java - Key sequence block management\n- FinancialUtils.java - Financial calculations and formatting\n\n### Test Files\n\n**45. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/test/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/TradeResourceTest.java**\n- Simple Quarkus test for market summary endpoint\n\n**46. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/test/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessagingTest.java**\n- Tests JMS to Reactive Messaging migration\n- Verifies broker/streamer ping, quote updates, and async orders\n\n**47. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/test/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessagingResourceTest.java**\n- REST API tests for messaging endpoints\n- Tests ping/broker, ping/streamer, stats collection\n\n## Key Migration Patterns Observed\n\n1. **javax.* -> jakarta.*** throughout all files\n2. **EJB Annotations -> CDI**: @Stateless/@Singleton -> @ApplicationScoped\n3. **Transaction Management**: @TransactionAttribute -> @Transactional\n4. **JMS -> Reactive Messaging**: Complete replacement with SmallRye Reactive Messaging\n5. **ManagedExecutorService -> Virtual Threads**: @VirtualThreads ExecutorService\n6. **ID Generation**: Simplified to IDENTITY strategy for Quarkus\n7. **Servlets -> JAX-RS**: Web layer modernization\n8. **DataSource Injection**: @Resource -> @Inject AgroalDataSource\n\nThe migration preserves all business logic while modernizing the infrastructure for Quarkus."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"526dd82c-65bb-41d2-a67a-297348d137d4"}
