{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01QPVeQshChbXkVx9wPgrxgy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_014dRW8TRwfH5NNWLDAN3PYJ","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create Jakarta EE config files","prompt":"I need you to create several configuration files for a Jakarta EE application being migrated from Quarkus to run on Open Liberty. The project root is at:\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output\n\nCreate the following files using the Write tool:\n\n1. **src/main/liberty/config/server.xml** - Open Liberty server configuration:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<server description=\"DayTrader Jakarta EE Server\">\n\n    <featureManager>\n        <feature>jakartaee-10.0</feature>\n        <feature>mpConfig-3.1</feature>\n        <feature>localConnector-1.0</feature>\n    </featureManager>\n\n    <httpEndpoint id=\"defaultHttpEndpoint\"\n                  httpPort=\"8080\"\n                  httpsPort=\"8443\" />\n\n    <!-- H2 Database Library -->\n    <library id=\"h2Lib\">\n        <fileset dir=\"${server.config.dir}/lib\" includes=\"h2*.jar\"/>\n    </library>\n\n    <!-- DataSource Configuration -->\n    <dataSource id=\"TradeDataSource\" jndiName=\"jdbc/TradeDataSource\">\n        <jdbcDriver libraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n        <properties.h2.embedded databaseName=\"mem:tradedb\" createDatabase=\"true\" user=\"sa\" password=\"\"/>\n    </dataSource>\n\n    <!-- JMS Configuration using embedded messaging -->\n    <wasJmsEndpoint id=\"InboundJmsCommsEndpoint\" wasJmsPort=\"7276\" wasJmsSSLPort=\"9100\"/>\n    \n    <jmsActivationSpec id=\"daytrader/DTBroker3MDB\">\n        <properties.wasJms destinationType=\"jakarta.jms.Queue\" destinationRef=\"TradeBrokerQueue\"/>\n    </jmsActivationSpec>\n    \n    <jmsActivationSpec id=\"daytrader/DTStreamer3MDB\">\n        <properties.wasJms destinationType=\"jakarta.jms.Topic\" destinationRef=\"TradeStreamerTopic\"/>\n    </jmsActivationSpec>\n    \n    <jmsQueue id=\"TradeBrokerQueue\" jndiName=\"jms/TradeBrokerQueue\">\n        <properties.wasJms queueName=\"TradeBrokerQueue\"/>\n    </jmsQueue>\n    \n    <jmsTopic id=\"TradeStreamerTopic\" jndiName=\"jms/TradeStreamerTopic\">\n        <properties.wasJms topicName=\"TradeStreamerTopic\"/>\n    </jmsTopic>\n    \n    <jmsConnectionFactory id=\"QueueConnectionFactory\" jndiName=\"jms/QueueConnectionFactory\">\n        <properties.wasJms/>\n    </jmsConnectionFactory>\n    \n    <jmsConnectionFactory id=\"TopicConnectionFactory\" jndiName=\"jms/TopicConnectionFactory\">\n        <properties.wasJms/>\n    </jmsConnectionFactory>\n\n    <messagingEngine>\n        <queue id=\"TradeBrokerQueue\"/>\n        <topicSpace id=\"TradeStreamerTopic\"/>\n    </messagingEngine>\n\n    <!-- Application -->\n    <webApplication id=\"daytrader\" location=\"daytrader.war\" contextRoot=\"/\">\n        <classloader apiTypeVisibility=\"+third-party\" commonLibraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n    </webApplication>\n\n    <logging consoleLogLevel=\"INFO\"/>\n</server>\n```\n\n2. **src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml** - JPA persistence configuration:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<persistence version=\"3.0\" xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence\"\n             xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n             xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_3_0.xsd\">\n    <persistence-unit name=\"daytrader\" transaction-type=\"JTA\">\n        <jta-data-source>jdbc/TradeDataSource</jta-data-source>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountProfileDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.HoldingDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.OrderDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.QuoteDataBean</class>\n        <properties>\n            <property name=\"jakarta.persistence.schema-generation.database.action\" value=\"drop-and-create\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.dialect\" value=\"org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.show_sql\" value=\"false\"/>\n        </properties>\n    </persistence-unit>\n</persistence>\n```\n\n3. **src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml** - Web deployment descriptor:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<web-app xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n         xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/web-app_6_0.xsd\"\n         version=\"6.0\">\n    \n    <display-name>DayTrader Jakarta EE</display-name>\n</web-app>\n```\n\n4. **src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml** - CDI beans descriptor:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<beans xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/beans_4_0.xsd\"\n       version=\"4.0\"\n       bean-discovery-mode=\"all\">\n</beans>\n```\n\n5. **src/main/resources/META-INF/microprofile-config.properties** - MicroProfile Config properties:\n```properties\n# Trade Application Configuration\ntrade.runtime-mode=EJB3\ntrade.order-processing-mode=SYNCH\ntrade.max-users=50\ntrade.max-quotes=100\ntrade.db.populate.on.startup=true\n```\n\nPlease create all 5 files exactly as shown above. Use the Write tool for each.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2502,"cache_read_input_tokens":115137,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2502,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1847},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"a01aa51c-4a2e-468c-a00b-774e3450207b"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need you to create several configuration files for a Jakarta EE application being migrated from Quarkus to run on Open Liberty. The project root is at:\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output\n\nCreate the following files using the Write tool:\n\n1. **src/main/liberty/config/server.xml** - Open Liberty server configuration:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<server description=\"DayTrader Jakarta EE Server\">\n\n    <featureManager>\n        <feature>jakartaee-10.0</feature>\n        <feature>mpConfig-3.1</feature>\n        <feature>localConnector-1.0</feature>\n    </featureManager>\n\n    <httpEndpoint id=\"defaultHttpEndpoint\"\n                  httpPort=\"8080\"\n                  httpsPort=\"8443\" />\n\n    <!-- H2 Database Library -->\n    <library id=\"h2Lib\">\n        <fileset dir=\"${server.config.dir}/lib\" includes=\"h2*.jar\"/>\n    </library>\n\n    <!-- DataSource Configuration -->\n    <dataSource id=\"TradeDataSource\" jndiName=\"jdbc/TradeDataSource\">\n        <jdbcDriver libraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n        <properties.h2.embedded databaseName=\"mem:tradedb\" createDatabase=\"true\" user=\"sa\" password=\"\"/>\n    </dataSource>\n\n    <!-- JMS Configuration using embedded messaging -->\n    <wasJmsEndpoint id=\"InboundJmsCommsEndpoint\" wasJmsPort=\"7276\" wasJmsSSLPort=\"9100\"/>\n    \n    <jmsActivationSpec id=\"daytrader/DTBroker3MDB\">\n        <properties.wasJms destinationType=\"jakarta.jms.Queue\" destinationRef=\"TradeBrokerQueue\"/>\n    </jmsActivationSpec>\n    \n    <jmsActivationSpec id=\"daytrader/DTStreamer3MDB\">\n        <properties.wasJms destinationType=\"jakarta.jms.Topic\" destinationRef=\"TradeStreamerTopic\"/>\n    </jmsActivationSpec>\n    \n    <jmsQueue id=\"TradeBrokerQueue\" jndiName=\"jms/TradeBrokerQueue\">\n        <properties.wasJms queueName=\"TradeBrokerQueue\"/>\n    </jmsQueue>\n    \n    <jmsTopic id=\"TradeStreamerTopic\" jndiName=\"jms/TradeStreamerTopic\">\n        <properties.wasJms topicName=\"TradeStreamerTopic\"/>\n    </jmsTopic>\n    \n    <jmsConnectionFactory id=\"QueueConnectionFactory\" jndiName=\"jms/QueueConnectionFactory\">\n        <properties.wasJms/>\n    </jmsConnectionFactory>\n    \n    <jmsConnectionFactory id=\"TopicConnectionFactory\" jndiName=\"jms/TopicConnectionFactory\">\n        <properties.wasJms/>\n    </jmsConnectionFactory>\n\n    <messagingEngine>\n        <queue id=\"TradeBrokerQueue\"/>\n        <topicSpace id=\"TradeStreamerTopic\"/>\n    </messagingEngine>\n\n    <!-- Application -->\n    <webApplication id=\"daytrader\" location=\"daytrader.war\" contextRoot=\"/\">\n        <classloader apiTypeVisibility=\"+third-party\" commonLibraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n    </webApplication>\n\n    <logging consoleLogLevel=\"INFO\"/>\n</server>\n```\n\n2. **src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml** - JPA persistence configuration:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<persistence version=\"3.0\" xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence\"\n             xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n             xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_3_0.xsd\">\n    <persistence-unit name=\"daytrader\" transaction-type=\"JTA\">\n        <jta-data-source>jdbc/TradeDataSource</jta-data-source>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountProfileDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.HoldingDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.OrderDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.QuoteDataBean</class>\n        <properties>\n            <property name=\"jakarta.persistence.schema-generation.database.action\" value=\"drop-and-create\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.dialect\" value=\"org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect\"/>\n            <property name=\"hibernate.show_sql\" value=\"false\"/>\n        </properties>\n    </persistence-unit>\n</persistence>\n```\n\n3. **src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml** - Web deployment descriptor:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<web-app xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n         xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/web-app_6_0.xsd\"\n         version=\"6.0\">\n    \n    <display-name>DayTrader Jakarta EE</display-name>\n</web-app>\n```\n\n4. **src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml** - CDI beans descriptor:\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<beans xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee\"\n       xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n       xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee/beans_4_0.xsd\"\n       version=\"4.0\"\n       bean-discovery-mode=\"all\">\n</beans>\n```\n\n5. **src/main/resources/META-INF/microprofile-config.properties** - MicroProfile Config properties:\n```properties\n# Trade Application Configuration\ntrade.runtime-mode=EJB3\ntrade.order-processing-mode=SYNCH\ntrade.max-users=50\ntrade.max-quotes=100\ntrade.db.populate.on.startup=true\n```\n\nPlease create all 5 files exactly as shown above. Use the Write tool for each."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014dRW8TRwfH5NNWLDAN3PYJ","session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"a93a5488-e6cb-4115-b86c-03e989bb0a93"}
