{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JJjjxYv4DSQomCdZqKkaoq","type":"tool_result","content":"    30→\n    31→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n    32→import jakarta.inject.Inject;\n    33→import javax.sql.DataSource;\n    34→\n    35→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.beans.RunStatsDataBean;\n    36→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountDataBean;\n    37→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.TradeDB;\n    38→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.TradeJDBC;\n    39→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.TradeServices;\n    40→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.Log;\n    41→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.MDBStats;\n    42→import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.TradeConfig;\n    43→\n    44→/**\n    45→ * TradeBuildDB uses operations provided by the TradeApplication to (a) create the Database tables\n    46→ * (b)populate a DayTrader database without creating the tables. Specifically, a\n    47→ * new DayTrader User population is created using UserIDs of the form \"uid:xxx\"\n    48→ * where xxx is a sequential number (e.g. uid:0, uid:1, etc.). New stocks are also created of the\n    49→ * form \"s:xxx\", again where xxx represents sequential numbers (e.g. s:1, s:2, etc.)\n    50→ */\n    51→@ApplicationScoped\n    52→public class TradeDirectDBUtils implements TradeDB {\n    53→\n    54→  // MIGRATION: @Inject AgroalDataSource -> @Resource DataSource\n    55→  @Resource(lookup = \"jdbc/TradeDataSource\")\n    56→  javax.sql.DataSource datasource;\n    57→\n    58→  @Inject \n    59→  @TradeJDBC\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"1db034be-34ec-4e4b-aaa1-adc41ef63d7b"}
