{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GxUoBc8xYBhei7w5kUpvNQ","type":"tool_result","content":"    40→@Singleton\n    41→@Startup\n    42→public class DatabasePopulator {\n    43→\n    44→    @PersistenceContext(unitName = \"daytrader\")\n    45→    EntityManager em;\n    46→\n    47→    @Inject\n    48→    @ConfigProperty(name = \"trade.db.populate.on.startup\", defaultValue = \"true\")\n    49→    boolean populateOnStartup;\n    50→\n    51→    @Inject\n    52→    @ConfigProperty(name = \"trade.max.users\", defaultValue = \"50\")\n    53→    int maxUsers;\n    54→\n    55→    @Inject\n    56→    @ConfigProperty(name = \"trade.max.quotes\", defaultValue = \"100\")\n    57→    int maxQuotes;\n    58→\n    59→    @PostConstruct\n    60→    @TransactionAttribute(TransactionAttributeType.REQUIRED)\n    61→    void onStart() {\n    62→        if (!populateOnStartup) {\n    63→            Log.log(\"Database population disabled via configuration\");\n    64→            return;\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"76a7554f-0e2d-485b-917e-cdc41fb1255d"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01MMMG4WkrTT2SULGVQtedG7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `@ConfigProperty` with primitives can be problematic. Let me also check - the `@TransactionAttribute` on `@PostConstruct` may not work as expected on a `@Singleton` - the default transaction management is already container-managed with REQUIRED. Let me make sure the imports are all correct in DatabasePopulator:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":614,"cache_read_input_tokens":89659,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":614,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":201},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"4c0f39d6-d0fa-4b1c-aa81-8d1ad5adc759"}
