{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01BgP9Hd9wMFpPmazn5MFQzm","type":"tool_result","content":"Internal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Table \"ACCOUNTEJB\" not found; SQL statement:\nALTER TABLE accountejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_accountejb_PROFILE_USERID FOREIGN KEY (PROFILE_USERID) REFERENCES accountprofileejb (USERID) [42102-224]\nError Code: 42102\nCall: ALTER TABLE accountejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_accountejb_PROFILE_USERID FOREIGN KEY (PROFILE_USERID) REFERENCES accountprofileejb (USERID)\nQuery: DataModifyQuery(sql=\"ALTER TABLE accountejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_accountejb_PROFILE_USERID FOREIGN KEY (PROFILE_USERID) REFERENCES accountprofileejb (USERID)\")\n[WARNING ] CWWJP9991W: Exception [EclipseLink-4002] (Eclipse Persistence Services - 4.0.9.v202601021151-061974965b9a70b72fdcb96dae36a4d6ef5df9ce): org.eclipse.persistence.exceptions.DatabaseException\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Table \"HOLDINGEJB\" not found; SQL statement:\nALTER TABLE holdingejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_holdingejb_QUOTE_SYMBOL FOREIGN KEY (QUOTE_SYMBOL) REFERENCES quoteejb (SYMBOL) [42102-224]\nError Code: 42102\nCall: ALTER TABLE holdingejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_holdingejb_QUOTE_SYMBOL FOREIGN KEY (QUOTE_SYMBOL) REFERENCES quoteejb (SYMBOL)\nQuery: DataModifyQuery(sql=\"ALTER TABLE holdingejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_holdingejb_QUOTE_SYMBOL FOREIGN KEY (QUOTE_SYMBOL) REFERENCES quoteejb (SYMBOL)\")\n[WARNING ] CWWJP9991W: Exception [EclipseLink-4002] (Eclipse Persistence Services - 4.0.9.v202601021151-061974965b9a70b72fdcb96dae36a4d6ef5df9ce): org.eclipse.persistence.exceptions.DatabaseException\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Table \"ORDEREJB\" not found; SQL statement:\nALTER TABLE orderejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_orderejb_ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID FOREIGN KEY (ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID) REFERENCES accountejb (ACCOUNTID) [42102-224]\nError Code: 42102\nCall: ALTER TABLE orderejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_orderejb_ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID FOREIGN KEY (ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID) REFERENCES accountejb (ACCOUNTID)\nQuery: DataModifyQuery(sql=\"ALTER TABLE orderejb ADD CONSTRAINT FK_orderejb_ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID FOREIGN KEY (ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID) REFERENCES accountejb (ACCOUNTID)\")\n[INFO    ] WELD-000411: Observer method [BackedAnnotatedMethod] org.apache.myfaces.config.annotation.CdiAnnotationProviderExtension.processAnnotatedType(@Observes ProcessAnnotatedType<T>) receives events for all annotated types. Consider restricting events using @WithAnnotations or a generic type with bounds.\n--\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Table \"ACCOUNTEJB\" not found; SQL statement:","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"107e601d-fa64-4ff4-94e7-ac6ae51a2412"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_016WsmTdvXL1kzMbVPcHdcXW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I see the problem clearly! EclipseLink is trying to do DDL (CREATE TABLE and ALTER TABLE for FK constraints), but the ALTER TABLE statements fail because the tables don't exist. This suggests the CREATE TABLE statements for `accountejb`, `holdingejb`, `orderejb` are failing silently, while `quoteejb` and `accountprofileejb` are being created successfully.\n\nThe issue is likely with the H2 database and how EclipseLink generates DDL. The `ACCOUNTEJB` table has a OneToOne FK to `ACCOUNTPROFILEEJB`, so it could be a circular dependency or ordering issue with EclipseLink DDL generation.\n\nLooking at the pattern: `quoteejb` (no FKs pointing out) was created, and population of quotes worked. But `accountejb` (has FK to `accountprofileejb`) couldn't be created. This is an EclipseLink issue.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use EclipseLink's native DDL generation instead of Jakarta standard:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1203,"cache_read_input_tokens":147549,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1203,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":849},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"87d4696b-9dd5-4032-b656-ba9cfdc865a2"}
