{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_019L49xAhS4vF3JguvFKPcQw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There are new issues:\n1. **ORB user registry not available within 10 seconds** - even though we added `<basicRegistry>`, it seems the timing is off. The EJB module takes too long, and the registry wasn't ready.\n2. **DataSource detection** - EclipseLink can't detect the platform because when the DatabasePopulator (BMT Singleton) tries to access the DataSource, it goes through the JNDI resource factory before the datasource is fully initialized.\n\nThe 30-second timeout suggests the app is hanging during startup. Let me look more carefully at the errors:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":898,"cache_read_input_tokens":133020,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":898,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":237},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"476bc041-c68b-448c-94a3-4b02717384ad"}
