{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012VDbfKUbVQGysKh9NXCGe9","type":"tool_result","content":"Query: InsertObjectQuery(AccountDataBean [accountID=null, loginCount=0, logoutCount=0, lastLogin=2026-03-14 18:28:58.108, creationDate=2026-03-14 18:28:58.108, balance=253133, openBalance=253133])\n[ERROR   ] Error: TradeBuildDB: Error populating database\n\t\n\tjakarta.persistence.PersistenceException: Exception [EclipseLink-4002] (Eclipse Persistence Services - 4.0.9.v202601021151-061974965b9a70b72fdcb96dae36a4d6ef5df9ce): org.eclipse.persistence.exceptions.DatabaseException\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Table \"ACCOUNTEJB\" not found; SQL statement:\nINSERT INTO accountejb (BALANCE, CREATIONDATE, LASTLOGIN, LOGINCOUNT, LOGOUTCOUNT, OPENBALANCE, PROFILE_USERID) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?) [42102-224]\nError Code: 42102\nCall: INSERT INTO accountejb (BALANCE, CREATIONDATE, LASTLOGIN, LOGINCOUNT, LOGOUTCOUNT, OPENBALANCE, PROFILE_USERID) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\n\tbind => [7 parameters bound]\nQuery: InsertObjectQuery(AccountDataBean [accountID=null, loginCount=0, logoutCount=0, lastLogin=2026-03-14 18:28:58.108, creationDate=2026-03-14 18:28:58.108, balance=253133, openBalance=253133])\njakarta.persistence.PersistenceException: Exception [EclipseLink-4002] (Eclipse Persistence Services - 4.0.9.v202601021151-061974965b9a70b72fdcb96dae36a4d6ef5df9ce): org.eclipse.persistence.exceptions.DatabaseException\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Table \"ACCOUNTEJB\" not found; SQL statement:\nINSERT INTO accountejb (BALANCE, CREATIONDATE, LASTLOGIN, LOGINCOUNT, LOGOUTCOUNT, OPENBALANCE, PROFILE_USERID) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?) [42102-224]\nError Code: 42102\nCall: INSERT INTO accountejb (BALANCE, CREATIONDATE, LASTLOGIN, LOGINCOUNT, LOGOUTCOUNT, OPENBALANCE, PROFILE_USERID) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\n\tbind => [7 parameters bound]\nQuery: InsertObjectQuery(AccountDataBean [accountID=null, loginCount=0, logoutCount=0, lastLogin=2026-03-14 18:28:58.108, creationDate=2026-03-14 18:28:58.108, balance=253133, openBalance=253133])\n\tat org.eclipse.persistence.internal.jpa.EntityManagerImpl.flush(EntityManagerImpl.java:967)\n\tat [internal classes]\n\tat com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.startup.DatabasePopulator.populateUsers(DatabasePopulator.java:139)\n\tat com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.startup.DatabasePopulator.onStart(DatabasePopulator.java:67)\n\tat java.base/jdk.internal.reflect.NativeMethodAccessorImpl.invoke0(Native Method)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"451204e2-0e81-4b5b-8754-cc90fc45f2d0"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0125XrGBge9UswZ4kFo2FGP8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Interesting! The JDBC table creation at line `stmt.executeUpdate(\"CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS accountejb (...)\")` reports success, but EclipseLink says `Table \"ACCOUNTEJB\" not found`. This means the tables created by our JDBC connection are in a different schema or connection context than what EclipseLink uses.\n\nThe issue is that H2 in-memory databases are per-connection by default. The JDBC connection from `dataSource.getConnection()` creates tables in one in-memory connection, but EclipseLink's EntityManager uses a different connection from the container, which can't see those tables.\n\nWait - but quotes (using `quoteejb`) WERE inserted successfully! So the `quoteejb` table IS visible. The issue is specifically with `accountejb`. Let me look at this differently - the JDBC `CREATE TABLE` was successful for all tables, the `quoteejb` INSERT via JPA worked, but the `accountejb` INSERT doesn't work.\n\nThe issue might be that the `mem:tradedb` with `DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1` is the same database, but EclipseLink caches metadata. EclipseLink tried to discover the table schema during EMF initialization (before our JDBC `CREATE TABLE`) and cached that accountejb doesn't exist. Even though we created the table via JDBC, EclipseLink's internal cache thinks the table doesn't exist.\n\nThe solution: use EclipseLink's DDL generation to create tables, and don't try to do it ourselves. Let me use a different approach - use `eclipselink.ddl-generation` = `create-tables` which should create tables during EMF initialization:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":983,"cache_read_input_tokens":141377,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":983,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":961},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"300fb8e1-b672-4fdd-a310-e2c039d0a6af"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0125XrGBge9UswZ4kFo2FGP8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_019uro7d1HPcMuNGwnFCJ1s4","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml","content":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<persistence version=\"3.0\" xmlns=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence\"\n             xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n             xsi:schemaLocation=\"https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_3_0.xsd\">\n    <persistence-unit name=\"daytrader\" transaction-type=\"JTA\">\n        <jta-data-source>jdbc/TradeDataSource</jta-data-source>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountProfileDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.HoldingDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.OrderDataBean</class>\n        <class>com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.QuoteDataBean</class>\n        <exclude-unlisted-classes>true</exclude-unlisted-classes>\n        <properties>\n            <property name=\"eclipselink.target-database\" value=\"org.eclipse.persistence.platform.database.H2Platform\"/>\n            <property name=\"eclipselink.logging.level\" value=\"INFO\"/>\n            <property name=\"eclipselink.ddl-generation\" value=\"create-tables\"/>\n            <property name=\"eclipselink.ddl-generation.output-mode\" value=\"database\"/>\n            <property name=\"eclipselink.deploy-on-startup\" value=\"true\"/>\n        </properties>\n    </persistence-unit>\n</persistence>\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":983,"cache_read_input_tokens":141377,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":983,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":961},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"e1f9e931-4c52-443f-a8c9-21ffc6b0bce9"}
