{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01CVT9ZJt5R4T34Ye3VGp3qV","type":"tool_result","content":"[INFO    ] TradeBuildDB: Creating database tables via JPA native queries...\n[INFO    ] TradeBuildDB: Database tables created successfully\n[INFO    ] TradeBuildDB: Populating DayTrader Database on startup...\n[INFO    ] TradeBuildDB: Creating 100 Quotes...\n[INFO    ] TradeBuildDB: Quotes populated successfully\n[INFO    ] TradeBuildDB: Registering 50 Users...\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nError Code: 90022\nCall: CALL IDENTITY()\nQuery: ValueReadQuery(name=\"SEQ_GEN_IDENTITY\" sql=\"CALL IDENTITY()\")\n[ERROR   ] Error: TradeBuildDB: Error populating users\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nError Code: 90022\nCall: CALL IDENTITY()\nQuery: ValueReadQuery(name=\"SEQ_GEN_IDENTITY\" sql=\"CALL IDENTITY()\")\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nError Code: 90022\nCall: CALL IDENTITY()\nQuery: ValueReadQuery(name=\"SEQ_GEN_IDENTITY\" sql=\"CALL IDENTITY()\")\n\tat com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.startup.DatabasePopulator.populateUsers(DatabasePopulator.java:226)\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nError Code: 90022\nCall: CALL IDENTITY()\nQuery: ValueReadQuery(name=\"SEQ_GEN_IDENTITY\" sql=\"CALL IDENTITY()\")\norg.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nError Code: 90022\nCall: CALL IDENTITY()\nQuery: ValueReadQuery(name=\"SEQ_GEN_IDENTITY\" sql=\"CALL IDENTITY()\")\n\tat com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.startup.DatabasePopulator.populateUsers(DatabasePopulator.java:226)\nInternal Exception: org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]\nError Code: 90022\nCall: CALL IDENTITY()\nQuery: ValueReadQuery(name=\"SEQ_GEN_IDENTITY\" sql=\"CALL IDENTITY()\")\norg.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLSyntaxErrorException: Function \"IDENTITY\" not found; SQL statement:\nCALL IDENTITY() [90022-224]","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"7344f6b2-ad9b-44b3-a273-e8edc23c8d96"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_014tUQggjKHGSg3V8RdPbrC9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tables were created successfully. Quotes populated successfully (QuoteDataBean has String PK, no auto-increment). But `AccountDataBean` persist fails because EclipseLink's H2Platform uses `CALL IDENTITY()` to retrieve auto-generated IDs, which doesn't exist in H2 2.x.\n\nThe fix options are:\n1. **Switch ID generation to TABLE or SEQUENCE** strategy instead of IDENTITY\n2. **Use H2 compatibility mode** with `MODE=LEGACY` in the JDBC URL\n3. **Create an alias function** `IDENTITY()` in H2 that maps to the correct H2 2.x equivalent\n\nOption 2 is the simplest - H2's LEGACY mode restores the `IDENTITY()` function. Let me try that:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1282,"cache_read_input_tokens":53151,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1282,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":533},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"658d8994-21ab-4ecc-b932-eca180708b81"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_014tUQggjKHGSg3V8RdPbrC9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01RdiRFGUVzr879ViZUk9LME","name":"TodoWrite","input":{"todos":[{"content":"Fix H2 DataSource configuration in server.xml","status":"completed","activeForm":"Fixing H2 DataSource configuration"},{"content":"Fix persistence.xml for EclipseLink (not Hibernate)","status":"completed","activeForm":"Fixing persistence.xml for EclipseLink"},{"content":"Add basic user registry to server.xml","status":"completed","activeForm":"Adding user registry to server.xml"},{"content":"Disable EclipseLink DDL generation - let DatabasePopulator create tables","status":"completed","activeForm":"Disabling EclipseLink DDL, fixing table creation"},{"content":"Fix H2 2.x IDENTITY() compatibility with LEGACY mode","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Fixing H2 2.x IDENTITY() compatibility"},{"content":"Rebuild and verify full database population","status":"pending","activeForm":"Rebuilding and verifying database population"},{"content":"Run smoke tests against running container","status":"pending","activeForm":"Running smoke tests"},{"content":"Document everything in CHANGELOG.md","status":"pending","activeForm":"Documenting in CHANGELOG.md"}]}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1282,"cache_read_input_tokens":53151,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1282,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":533},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"80f33c9e-4b58-4aa3-9759-a14e47ee4b05"}
