{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Qg6wJ5CQM5waGqHJmzPgWJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The error is `null PK has been incorrectly provided for this find operation`. This happens in the `buy` method when `completeOrder` is called. Looking at the code: after `createOrder`, we call `completeOrder(orderID, false)`. The `orderID` is null because the order was just persisted and the IDENTITY-generated ID hasn't been flushed yet.\n\nLet me look at the `createOrder` method:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1544,"cache_read_input_tokens":109575,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1544,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":311},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"0df3948c-abb2-496b-ba15-a90efeb98515"}
