or destination Default.Topic.Space on bus defaultBus has been successfully created.\n[INFO    ]  CWSIV0556I: Connection to the Messaging Engine was successful. The message-driven bean with activation specification daytrader/DTStreamer3MDB will now be able to receive the messages from destination Default.Topic.Space.\n[INFO    ] J2CA8801I: The message endpoint for activation specification daytrader/DTStreamer3MDB and message driven bean application daytrader#daytrader.war#DTStreamer3MDB is activated.\n[INFO    ]  CWSIV0777I: A connection to messaging engine defaultME for destination TradeBrokerQueue on bus defaultBus has been successfully created.\n[INFO    ]  CWSIV0556I: Connection to the Messaging Engine was successful. The message-driven bean with activation specification daytrader/DTBroker3MDB will now be able to receive the messages from destination TradeBrokerQueue.\n[INFO    ] J2CA8801I: The message endpoint for activation specification daytrader/DTBroker3MDB and message driven bean application daytrader#daytrader.war#DTBroker3MDB is activated.\n[AUDIT   ] CWWKF0012I: The server installed the following features: [appAuthentication-3.0, appAuthorization-2.1, appClientSupport-2.0, appSecurity-5.0, batch-2.1, beanValidation-3.0, cdi-4.0, concurrent-3.0, connectors-2.1, distributedMap-1.0, enterpriseBeans-4.0, enterpriseBeansHome-4.0, enterpriseBeansLite-4.0, enterpriseBeansPersistentTimer-4.0, enterpriseBeansRemote-4.0, expressionLanguage-5.0, faces-4.0, jakartaee-10.0, jdbc-4.2, jndi-1.0, jsonb-3.0, jsonp-2.1, localConnector-1.0, mail-2.1, managedBeans-2.0, mdb-4.0, messaging-3.1, messagingClient-3.0, messagingSecurity-3.0, messagingServer-3.0, mpConfig-3.1, pages-3.1, persistence-3.1, persistenceContainer-3.1, restfulWS-3.1, restfulWSClient-3.1, servlet-6.0, ssl-1.0, transportSecurity-1.0, webProfile-10.0, websocket-2.1, xmlBinding-4.0, xmlWS-4.0].\n[INFO    ] CWWKF0008I: Feature update completed in 5.201 seconds.\n[AUDIT   ] CWWKF0011I: The defaultServer server is ready to run a smarter planet. The defaultServer server started in 5.815 seconds.\n[INFO    ] RESTEASY002225: Deploying jakarta.ws.rs.core.Application: class com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.jaxrs.JaxrsApplication$Proxy$_$$_WeldClientProxy\n[INFO    ] SRVE0242I: [daytrader] [/] [com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.jaxrs.JaxrsApplication]: Initialization successful.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"f52f6c97-a813-4b8a-b824-77af38aa1349"}
