{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01J7WQhuFoK2oJT9rfYwyDzU","type":"tool_result","content":"[SMOKE] Starting smoke tests against http://localhost:34157\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Market Summary ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/trade/market]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Get Quotes ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/quotes/s:0]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Get Multiple Quotes ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/quotes/s:0,s:1,s:2]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Login ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [POST /rest/trade/login]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Get Account ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/trade/account/uid:0]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Get Account Profile ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/trade/account/uid:0/profile]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Get Holdings ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/trade/account/uid:0/holdings]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Get Orders ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/trade/account/uid:0/orders]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Buy Stock ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [POST /rest/trade/buy]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Register ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [POST /rest/trade/register]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Logout ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [POST /rest/trade/logout/uid:0]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n--- Test: Web App Welcome ---\n[SMOKE]   PASS [GET /rest/app]: status=200\n[SMOKE] \n==================================================\n[SMOKE] RESULTS: 12/12 passed, 0/12 failed\n[SMOKE] ==================================================\n[SMOKE] ALL SMOKE TESTS PASSED","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc4c4d58-9b0e-47fb-9764-ecee6ff08c39","uuid":"aae32a06-5179-49fd-b4f1-a74ce9bf3d45"}
